dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Outagamie_Addresses_2018.gdb. [This is a NpointN feature class representing the location where the driveway meets the road right of way. It contains the House Number and Street Name (Address). The parcel number is also included for each address NpointN.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
